   <text>
      <body divRole="original-translation">
         <div type="original" xml:lang="nl">
            <pb xml:id="pb.orig.nl.1" f="1r" facs="#z1" n="1"/>
            <p xml:id="p.orig.nl.1" n="1">Den Haag</p>
            <p xml:id="p.orig.nl.2" n="2">Zaterdag</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p xml:id="p.orig.nl.3" n="3">Beste Jo,</p>
            <p xml:id="p.orig.nl.4" n="4">Ik ben blij dat ’t portretje je bevalt.<ptr type="note" target="#note.orig.nl.1"/> Ik kom volgende week graag eens. Zal ik dan meteen mijn Van Goghje halen?<ptr type="note" target="#note.orig.nl.2"/>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="p.orig.nl.5" n="5" rend="indent">Schrijf maar welke dagen je ’t beste kunt.</p>
            <p xml:id="p.orig.nl.6" n="6" rend="indent">Tot ziens,</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p xml:id="p.orig.nl.7" n="7">Yours</p>
            <p xml:id="p.orig.nl.8" n="8">Isaac</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <pb xml:id="pb.orig.nl.2" f="1r" facs="#z2" n="2"/>
            <p xml:id="p.orig.nl.9" n="9">Mevrouw J. Van Gogh</p>
            <p xml:id="p.orig.nl.10" n="10">Koninginneweg 77</p>
            <p xml:id="p.orig.nl.11" n="11">Amsterdam</p>
            <pb xml:id="pb.orig.nl.3" f="1v" facs="#s1v" n="3"/>
         </div>
         <div type="translation" xml:lang="en">
            <pb xml:id="pb.tr.en.1"
               corresp="#pb.orig.nl.1"
               f="1r"
               facs="#z1"
               n="1"/>
            <p xml:id="p.tr.en.1" corresp="#p.orig.nl.1" n="1">The Hague</p>
            <p xml:id="p.tr.en.2" corresp="#p.orig.nl.2" n="2">Saturday</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p xml:id="p.tr.en.3" corresp="#p.orig.nl.3" n="3">Dear Jo,</p>
            <p xml:id="p.tr.en.4" corresp="#p.orig.nl.4" n="4">I’m glad you like the little portrait.<ptr type="note" target="#note.tr.en.1"/> I’ll happily come next week. Shall I collect my little Van Gogh right away?<ptr type="note" target="#note.tr.en.2"/>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="p.tr.en.5" corresp="#p.orig.nl.5" n="5" rend="indent">Write and let me know which days are best for you.</p>
            <p xml:id="p.tr.en.6" corresp="#p.orig.nl.6" n="6" rend="indent">See you soon,</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p xml:id="p.tr.en.7" corresp="#p.orig.nl.7" n="7">Yours</p>
            <p xml:id="p.tr.en.8" corresp="#p.orig.nl.8" n="8">Isaac</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <pb xml:id="pb.tr.en.2"
               corresp="#pb.orig.nl.2"
               f="1r"
               facs="#z2"
               n="2"/>
            <p xml:id="p.tr.en.9" corresp="#p.orig.nl.9" n="9">Mevrouw J. Van Gogh</p>
            <p xml:id="p.tr.en.10" corresp="#p.orig.nl.10" n="10">Koninginneweg 77</p>
            <p xml:id="p.tr.en.11" corresp="#p.orig.nl.11" n="11">Amsterdam</p>
            <pb xml:id="pb.tr.en.3" corresp="#pb.orig.nl.3" f="1v" facs="#s1v" n="3"/>
         </div>
      </body>
